{"tid":498224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我相信有好多人都諗過殺自己父母","createTime":"2017-12-13T15:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T16:37:08.000Z","uid":93124,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53de6eee5106cb78af77ce6987a2ade98be7de3f","tid":498224,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/221751_02aee4e21783c658c0f1580c6220fb2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F221751_02aee4e21783c658c0f1580c6220fb2f.jpg&h=7d7b592d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/221752_21121a8e99f431f7d2aadad3d2d270fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F221752_21121a8e99f431f7d2aadad3d2d270fc.jpg&h=62291309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說前兩日同fd入左場睇，見個poster以為係嗰啲典型勵志片啦，未姑且睇下stephy做成點，屌，完全唔係嗰回事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來個故事係以一單兇殺案為藍本，講個女仔係點樣殺自己既父母，睇到中段真係起曬雞皮！雖然成套劇既對白唔多，但係女主角既眼神真係好勁，好入戲，就算無咩血腥場面，但隔住個moon都smell到陣血味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為免劇透俾人問候老母，我都係唔講咁多內容⋯⋯純粹覺得呢套戲真係寫實得好恐怖，令我諗起好多自己既往事，尤其係我屋企人以前點樣對我⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  坦白講，我係好憎佢地，都曾經試過忍無可忍，想自殺了事。但係正如女主角所講，點解唔係我做錯，但死嗰個係我？我都有咁諗過，所以最後無做到。我同stephy既角色比較似，一味死忍，但個心係好痛恨屋企人。<br />\n<br />\n相信係香港，大把人既家庭關係差過我，表面好似好規矩導距既人，內心都總會有怨念，只不過呢一面得我地自已知⋯⋯女主角只不過係做左佢心中所想，用佢父母條命，換自己自由，所以睇睇下我竟然同情佢⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有無巴打明我呢種感受⋯⋯總之睇完呢套戲我真係幾沉重，但係又好配服個導演，點解可以揣摩兇手既心理揣摩得咁透徹？？？小弟真係欽敬欽敬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲人話stephy拍空手道，係佢歷來最好既表現，睇過藍天白藍既人就知，一定唔係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 不嬲都唔中意鄧麗欣同万力申，但係而家覺得佢幾好"},{"pid":"6bdabdd4a9cf5864f47c79bbe4467bae1168cb46","tid":498224,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"邊鳩個万力申<br />\n万刀甲就識"},{"pid":"14e89a03d4e29143bc16be9a7cebe7cde7c556e2","tid":498224,"uid":128472,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"想殺家姐多過老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29144e934d2488e52e054e668f87568b8a64a5d5","tid":498224,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想殺家姐多過老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個case都聽得多"},{"pid":"2bdad2cf5a0029e3e2da9d8b85ddf07b51f6be1e","tid":498224,"uid":93124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊鳩個万力申<br />\n万刀甲就識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時手快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  覺唔覺佢地散左之後鄧麗欣好似發展得仲好左"}]}